  "content": "<p>Please follow the instructions below to recover your remaining time when ID changes.</p><p>Uninstall LetsVPN won't affect your device ID. However, reset the system will result in the change of device ID. If you didn't register an account, the remaining time of your original device might unfortunately disappear after the ID changes.</p><p>Please carefully read the instructions below and we will try our best to help you recover your remaining time. For other relevant information, please read <a href='/help/en/article/2' class='text-blue-600 hover:underline'>&lt;Use one subscription on multiple devices&gt;</a>.</p><p>To recover your account, we need the listed information below:</p><ol style='list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 2rem; margin: 1rem 0;'><li>Your current device ID</li><li>A screenshot of your purchase record</li><li>Your original device ID (Optional)</li></ol><p>If you don't know how to find purchase record, please read <a href='/help/en/article/22' class='text-blue-600 hover:underline'>&lt;How to find my purchase history&gt;</a>.</p><p>For security reasons, we are unable to help you if you can't provide the screenshot of your purchase record.</p><p>Please send us an email at <a href='mailto:letsvpn@rbox.me' class='text-blue-600 hover:underline'>letsvpn@rbox.me</a> with the listed information above, our staff will help you. Generally, it will take 1 business day for us to get back to you. Please don't hesitate to contact us if you have any problem.</p><div class='mt-8 bg-white p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 shadow-sm'><h3 class='text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2'>Related Articles</h3><ul><li class='border-b border-gray-200 last:border-b-0'><a href='/help/en/article/51' class='flex justify-between items-center py-3 text-gray-700 hover:text-brand-purple transition-colors'><span class='text-base'>Find the software version on my device</span><svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' class='h-5 w-5 text-gray-400' viewBox='0 0 20 20'